□ All analyst names and firms accurate (verify spelling if provided)

8. LEGAL COMPLIANCE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
□ No investment advice ("buy", "sell", "we recommend", "you should")
□ All recommendations attributed to analysts/management
